com.omerozer.knit

Class KnitNavigator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.omerozer.knit.KnitNavigator

  • public class KnitNavigator
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that handles Navigation accross all views. Instance is stored inside Knit and is often accessed inside KnitPresenter.getNavigator().
